{"tid":1697314,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關於斬妖義士","createTime":"2019-11-06T19:01:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T14:29:55.000Z","uid":279401,"like":37,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"bf01320a799cd847c4f176544f331074236ef2d4","tid":1697314,"uid":279401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T19:01:53.000Z","msg":"關於斬妖義士，如果我係義士，見到手足估係義士唔係義士係度互屌就真係好心痛！抗爭到今時今日，前線同義士都付出咁多，佢地係想得到咩野呀？係五大訴求呀！佢地承擔既後果唔係想睇到手足互屌、分化及繼而潰散！事情發生左，日後自然會知道佢自己點解做依件事，到時係唔係義士自有答案！依家確立佢係義士又如何? 幫到佢咩呀？定係你封佢係義士既光環既心靈安慰呀？我相信如果係義士，佢本人一定係希望佢既行動對抗爭有幫助！我地今次抗爭係贏撚硬，最怕係好人唔參與唔發聲但係樂於批評！手足立刻對準目標，向贏依盤仗出發！<br />\n抗爭就係對抗，要知己知彼！唔係要諸多批評互屌！錯只係需要交流修正！岩就坐言起行做應做既事！唔好只係希望贏，係要有香港人贏撚硬既心態！<br />\n<br />\n【政情】建制不信何君堯「苦肉計」 遇襲或成押後區選轉捩點<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=368978&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D368978%26refer%3DShare&d=40Eeu%2FLL1847%2FNonScroNf1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=77f93408\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D368978%26refer%3DShare&h=928cf81a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=368978&amp;refer=Share</a><br />\n<br />\n睇完政情就依家諗應該點做落去！<br />\n唔好再浪費青春互屌！"},{"pid":"51c7511e4afb49e15c76a0dbed44bdd09f07484e","tid":1697314,"uid":225098,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T19:04:49.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">中華蘇維埃共和國<br />\n成立於<span style=\"color: red;\">1931年11月7日</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cBZm2QR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcBZm2QR.png&h=566ea80d&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n1931年12月1日，毛澤東、項英、張國燾聯名於《中華蘇維埃共和國中央執行委員會布告》表明在一個中國疆域內有<span style=\"color: red;\">兩國</span>：「從現在起，中國疆域內有不同的兩國。一個是中華民國，是帝國主義的工具。另一是中華蘇維埃共和國，是剝削與壓迫下廣大工農兵的國家，他的旗幟是<span style=\"color: red;\">打倒帝國主義、消滅地主階級、推翻國民黨軍閥政府、建立蘇維埃政府於全中國，為數萬萬被壓迫被剝削的工農兵士及其他被壓迫群眾的利益而奮鬥，為全國真正的和平統一而奮鬥</span>。」。"},{"pid":"a7265a1602ee3dd2e2b38fba0c2fcdc3aaea680d","tid":1697314,"uid":225488,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T19:36:49.000Z","msg":"感謝義士"},{"pid":"c17d808a02af191695c394becf60e95e091b3aa6","tid":1697314,"uid":279401,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7265a1602ee3dd2e2b38fba0c2fcdc3aaea680d","tid":1697314,"uid":225488,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T19:36:49.000Z","msg":"感謝義士"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T19:44:30.000Z","msg":"未確定係唔係！個人相信！"},{"pid":"8ab136450214cc1f8f1dfb53af1ed8c4b1524e7f","tid":1697314,"uid":317919,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T19:47:48.000Z","msg":"炒車就改善 光速割蓆咪認衰仔 互屌有咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02c1f51d2a7da1a481ed19f7159265a09c6e6086","tid":1697314,"uid":279401,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ab136450214cc1f8f1dfb53af1ed8c4b1524e7f","tid":1697314,"uid":317919,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T19:47:48.000Z","msg":"炒車就改善 光速割蓆咪認衰仔 互屌有咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T19:48:59.000Z","msg":"做對抗爭有利應做既事！"},{"pid":"88f608d0bdf293de7665365d20a3995480a83191","tid":1697314,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T19:50:47.000Z","msg":"百屌成材(希望啦), 唔屌唔鬆化"},{"pid":"8b869c22672eb1f35622e2fa74f968881288c7c0","tid":1697314,"uid":279401,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"88f608d0bdf293de7665365d20a3995480a83191","tid":1697314,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T19:50:47.000Z","msg":"百屌成材(希望啦), 唔屌唔鬆化"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T19:52:37.000Z","msg":"哈哈！唔屌唔鬆化！"},{"pid":"